The paper discusses a stylized duopoly model in which two firms deploy multi-armed bandit algorithms and compete for myopic users. This suggests that the paper is likely to belong to the Game Theory (cs.GT), Machine Learning (cs.LG), Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI), Multi-Agent Systems (cs.MA), or Economics and Computation (cs.EC) sub-categories.
